contents.name: Kota
contents.page:
Kota command categories

Required Permissions: Read/Send, Embed Links, Add Reactions.

Category Description Usage
Animals Contains commands such as dog, cat k!help Animals
Announcements Contains commands such as quickpost k!help Announcements
Captcha Contains commands such as captcha, captcha set k!help Captcha
Dailyquotes Contains commands such as dailyquotes, dailyquotes set k!help Dailyquotes
Logging Contains commands such as logging, logging standard, logging modlogs k!help Logging
Prefixes Contains commands such as prefix, prefix add, prefix remove k!help Prefixes
Fun Contains commands such as coinflip, slots k!help Fun
Information Contains commands such as invite, about k!help Informations
Social Contains commands such as hug, kiss, pat k!help Social
Levels Contains commands such as level, leaderboard, levelquotes set k!help Levels
MISC Contains commands such as syntax k!help MISC
Moderator Contains commands such as warn, ban k!help Moderator
Music Contains commands such as play, queue k!help Music
Polls Contains commands such as poll, quickpoll k!help Polls
Quotes Contains commands such as anger, trust k!help Quotes
RoleAssign Contains commands such as selfroles, give, take k!help RoleAssign
Welcomer Contains commands such as welcomer, welcomer set k!help Welcomer
Utility Contains commands such as serverinfo k!help Utility
